  <title>The molecular genetics of virulence of Xanthomonas campestris</title>
  <URL>https://cn.bing.com/academic/profile?id=0c9c0fa4a38c36553a71b945ecbdbb73&amp;encoded=0&amp;v=paper_preview&amp;mkt=zh-cn</URL>
